  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"content\"\u003e\n\n\u003carticle\u003e\n\n\t\n \t\n \t\n\n \t\n\n \t\n\t\t\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eThese BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch are one of my favorite spins on the classic BLT. They are super delicious and wonderful to have for lunch in the summer! Crunchy, creamy, juicy from the tomatoes and so satisfying.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eNothing makes me happier than BLT wraps for lunch!\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch\" width=\"1670\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/blt-wraps/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"BLT Wraps with Jalapeño Ranch.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-scaled.jpg 1670w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-728x959.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-768x1012.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-1166x1536.jpg 1166w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-1554x2048.jpg 1554w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-150x198.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1670px) 100vw, 1670px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eThese BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch are such a fun twist on the classic. They are super satisfying, light and refreshing and have a little pop of heat. The jalapeno ranch is a spin on my \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2022/04/ranch-dressing-recipe/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eclassic ranch\