025/07/BLT-wraps-5-scaled.jpg 1649w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-728x971.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-1151x1536.jpg 1151w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-1535x2048.jpg 1535w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-640x853.jpg 640w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-150x200.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1649px) 100vw, 1649px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201649%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-scaled.jpg 1649w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-728x971.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-768x1024.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-1151x1536.jpg 1151w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-1535x2048.jpg 1535w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-640x853.jpg 640w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-150x200.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-5-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eYou can also make these for a little lunch party – make a few wraps in advance and slice them in half before serving. As long as you don’t drench them in ranch, the bacon stays really crispy! \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch\" width=\"1864\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data