/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch\" width=\"1800\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/blt-wraps/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"BLT Wraps with Jalapeño Ranch.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-scaled.jpg 1800w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-728x890.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-768x939.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-1256x1536.jpg 1256w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-1675x2048.jpg 1675w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-150x183.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201800%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-scaled.jpg 1800w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-728x890.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-768x939.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-1256x1536.jpg 1256w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-1675x2048.jpg 1675w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-150x183.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-8-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2\u003eBLT Wraps with Jalapeño Ranch\u003c/h2\u003e\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-100267\" data-recipe-id=\"100267\" data-servings=\"0\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-250x250.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-12-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eBLT Wraps with Jalapeno Ranch\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e30\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThese BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch are one of my favorite spins on the classic BLT. They are super delicious and wonderful to have for lunch in the summer! Crunchy, creamy, juicy from the tomatoes and so satisfying.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-100267-ingredients\" data-recipe=\"100267\" data-servings=\"0\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e12\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eslices\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/applegate-natural-uncured-sunday-bacon-8oz/-/A-14871957?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebacon\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003echopped romaine lettuce\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2 to 3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etomatoes,\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esliced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eburrito-size tortillas\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003ejalapeño ranch\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/jalapenos-10oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-82675341?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ejalapeño pepper,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eseeded and diced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eplain greek yogurt or sour cream\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/duke-39-s-real-smooth-38-creamy-mayonnaise-30-fl-oz/-/A-14776644?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003emayonnaise\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"9\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/2-reduced-fat-milk-1gal-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-13276204?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003emilk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"10\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e3\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efresh chives or 1 tablespoon dried chives\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"11\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efresh dill or 2 teaspoons dried dill weed\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"12\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efresh parsley or 1 teaspoon dried parsley\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"13\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e2\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/lemon-each/-/A-15013629?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003efresh lemon juice\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"14\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/garlic-powder-3-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77585075?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"15\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/onion-powder-2-62oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77588040\u0026amp;aflt=plt?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eonion powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"16\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e¼\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/smoked-spanish-paprika-2-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-84669679?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003esmoked paprika\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"17\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003epinch\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"recipe-100267-instructions\" data-recipe=\"100267\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100267-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the bacon in a large skillet over medium-low heat. Cook until it is crispy and the fat is rendered. Transfer the bacon to a paper towel to remove the excess grease.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100267-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo build the wraps, add 1 cup of romaine in the center. Drizzle a few tablespoons of the ranch over the romaine. Top with a few tomato slices (as many as you’d like!) and add a sprinkle of salt and pepper. Top with the bacon. Fold up the top and the bottom of the tortilla, then roll the sides in tightly to wrap it up.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100267-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eServe with extra ranch for dipping!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch4\u003ejalapeño ranch\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-100267-step-1-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd all ingredients to a blender or food processor and blend until pureed and combined. Store in the fridge in a sealed container. It will make more than needed! This lasts for about a week.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"BLT wraps with jalapeno ranch\" width=\"1768\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/07/blt-wraps/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"BLT Wraps with Jalapeño Ranch.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-scaled.jpg 1768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-728x906.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-768x956.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-1234x1536.jpg 1234w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-1646x2048.jpg 1646w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-150x187.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1768px) 100vw, 1768px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201768%202200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-scaled.jpg 1768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-728x906.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-768x956.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-1234x1536.jpg 1234w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-1646x2048.jpg 1646w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-150x187.jpg 150w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/BLT-wraps-13-scaled.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eP.S. while we’re on the topic of BLTs… \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/08/pimento-cheese-blts/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ea pimento cheese BLT\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e is pretty fantastic too. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\u003c/article\u003e \n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
